            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Bellomus"
                            >Bellomo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Villanus"
                                >Villano</name></persName> vende <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Leo">Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abate</rs> del <rs key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di
                            <orgName key="#Houses #Monasteries #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71">San Ponziano</orgName> di <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Lucca</placeName>, e a <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Giovanni</name></persName>, rector de <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >hospitale</rs> suprascripti Sancti Pontiani, quartam portionem di una
                            <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> et res massaricias posta in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3305">Stabbiano ubi dicitur a la
                            Leccia</placeName>, tenuta da <persName><name ref="Stephanus"
                                >Stefano</name></persName> massarium, que mihi per <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartula</rs> scripta ex manibus del <rs
                            key="#Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName>
                        ex donatione obvenit da <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Raginmundus"
                                >Raimondo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> del <persName key="#Notary">fu <name
                                ref="Petrus/Petraccus">Pietro</name> detto Petracco</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs>, ricevendo <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">meritum anulum unum aureo</rs> pro 90
                        soldi dal <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>. Chiede al <rs
                            key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Cuneradus"
                            >Corrado</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum Luca. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> del fu
                                <persName><name ref="Cunitius">Cunizio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Fuscus">Fosco</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Moronctus">Moronto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Lampertus">Lamberto</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
